{"tid":1919713,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"速剪髮型屋 戴口罩剪頭髮客人被剪掉口罩橡筋後大發雷霆","createTime":"2020-03-11T03:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T03:55:18.000Z","uid":6783,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93d80d9e82bdbb39c7fa8efc5d1c18407b31d324","tid":1919713,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:22:00.000Z","msg":"元朗一間日式單剪髮型屋因肺炎而在門口張貼告示聲稱「戴住口罩都剪得！」以招來客人。但髮型師未知係咪分唔到橡筋同頭髮，竟然錯手將口罩橡筋剪掉，口罩即時脫落。68歲男客人破口大罵後更報警求助，出手想搶掉剪刀意圖以牙還牙。一名男途人見狀立即制服暴徒，但警員三十分鐘後仍然未見蹤影，途人散去。<br />\n<br />\n二零二零年三月十一日"},{"pid":"9668a353c7ddd7f8f9a1f5b7097b2cfdbaf55efc","tid":1919713,"uid":86316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"樓主今日煮咩食"},{"pid":"7066d0cf9c01c87bab683b1c41f9659ac835bdde","tid":1919713,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9668a353c7ddd7f8f9a1f5b7097b2cfdbaf55efc","tid":1919713,"uid":86316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"樓主今日煮咩食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"口罩橡筋"},{"pid":"99ad3559fcc7ae5201c4716b383f37f4885090db","tid":1919713,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"搵唔到汁，定係我真心左"},{"pid":"38d0f205cc54e12d7d6759e7b2b3dbeed82a2200","tid":1919713,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9668a353c7ddd7f8f9a1f5b7097b2cfdbaf55efc","tid":1919713,"uid":86316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"樓主今日煮咩食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:30:29.000Z","msg":"中式牛柳&amp;豉油雞"},{"pid":"9870bf6bd0d4b46dc5cf4c71f0b81f90cf05c359","tid":1919713,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"送番個口罩比佢唔得?<br />\n條友戴n95?"},{"pid":"91220a1bb719641d9752018a8c76e51d3356e62c","tid":1919713,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"講明戴住口罩都剪得"},{"pid":"c2610